    <description>&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;FONT size=2&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;&lt;FONT color=#800000&gt;Brekkee -&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/STRONG&gt; *Porthias_FV* Will Spirit Shrouds be drops from MoBs or tradeskilled or how will u come to obtain \them? &lt;BR&gt;&lt;FONT color=#800000&gt;&lt;B&gt;Brekkee -&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt; [21:51] &lt;RYTAN&gt;I can take Porthias &lt;BR&gt;&lt;FONT color=#800000&gt;&lt;B&gt;Brekkee -&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt; Oops.. well yes.. he can &lt;BR&gt;&lt;FONT color=#800000&gt;&lt;B&gt;Brekkee -&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt; Forgive my mis-paste &lt;BR&gt;&lt;FONT color=#800080&gt;* Prathun teases Brekkee. *&lt;/FONT&gt; &lt;BR&gt;&lt;FONT color=#0000a0&gt;&lt;B&gt;Maddoc -&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt; Hehe &lt;BR&gt;&lt;FONT color=#0000a0&gt;&lt;B&gt;Maddoc -&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt; I got 5$ on Porthias &lt;BR&gt;&lt;FONT color=#0000a0&gt;&lt;B&gt;Rytan -&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt; Spirit shrouds are immediately available to every character as soon as they purchase DoD. You will have to play with the shrouds for a while before you can use some of the more powerful shrouds. &lt;BR&gt;&lt;FONT color=#0000a0&gt;&lt;B&gt;Rytan -&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt; hah! I win! &lt;BR&gt;&lt;FONT color=#0000a0&gt;&lt;B&gt;Kytherea -&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt; Occassionally we have to let you win Rytan &lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;FONT color=#800000&gt;&lt;B&gt;Brekkee -&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt; *Havenhawk* Are there plans for new melee disciplines for the 65+ crowd? &lt;BR&gt;&lt;FONT color=#0000a0&gt;&lt;B&gt;Rytan -&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt; Yes there is a new combat ability for each of the melee classes. Additionally, a few of the hybrids are getting new combat abilities with DoD as well. &lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;FONT color=#800000&gt;&lt;B&gt;Brekkee -&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt; *Leeroy* Will we be seeing more stories from the Wayfarer brotherhood in DoDh ? &lt;BR&gt;&lt;FONT color=#0000a0&gt;&lt;B&gt;AbsorEQ -&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt; This expansion doesn't involve the Wayfarers, though there's always the chance that they will again involve themselves in the story of Norrath. &lt;BR&gt;&lt;FONT color=#0000a0&gt;&lt;B&gt;Prathun -&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt; The Wayfarer's Brotherhood storyline doesn't intersect with Depths of Darkhollow. So, no. :) &lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;FONT color=#800000&gt;&lt;B&gt;Brekkee -&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt; *Jetfire* Will we be seeing the classic special mobs (Summoned, Undead, Animals) or will those of us with those special abilities be left out? &lt;BR&gt;&lt;FONT color=#0000a0&gt;&lt;B&gt;Rytan -&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt; Yes there will be examples of each of the various special NPC types such as summoned, animal, undead, etc. &lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;FONT color=#800000&gt;&lt;B&gt;Brekkee -&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt; *Ilsi* Will there be "cute" spirit shrouds as well as "scary" ones? &lt;BR&gt;&lt;FONT color=#0000a0&gt;&lt;B&gt;Rytan -&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt; Well I'm not really one to determine what's cute, but there are a few spirit shrouds that aren't your typical menacing monster. The fairy, the sporali, and several animals are available in addition to the more menacing monsters. &lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;FONT color=#800000&gt;&lt;B&gt;Brekkee -&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt; That will wrap it up for tonight. I'd like to thank our guests from EverQuest for coming! The log for tonight's chat will be up shortly on http://eq.stratics.com &lt;BR&gt;&lt;FONT color=#800000&gt;&lt;B&gt;Brekkee -&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt; Thank you all for joining us! You can join #EverQuest to chat more about the game. &lt;BR&gt;&lt;FONT color=#0000a0&gt;&lt;B&gt;Kytherea -&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt; Thank you for coming everyone! &lt;BR&gt;&lt;FONT color=#0000a0&gt;&lt;B&gt;Rashere -&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt; Thanks for the great questions everyone and have a wonderful evening. &lt;BR&gt;&lt;FONT color=#0000a0&gt;&lt;B&gt;Zorillius -&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt; Thanks everyone! &lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;FONT color=#800000&gt;&lt;B&gt;Brekkee -&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt; Hold on everyone! &lt;BR&gt;&lt;FONT color=#0000a0&gt;&lt;B&gt;Prathun -&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt; Thanks for joining us tonight, everyone! &lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;FONT color=#800000&gt;&lt;B&gt;Brekkee -&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt; We have a few beta keys to give away &lt;BR&gt;&lt;FONT color=#800000&gt;&lt;B&gt;Brekkee -&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt; put on your trivia hats and we will get started with that in just a moment &lt;BR&gt;&lt;FONT color=#800000&gt;&lt;B&gt;Brekkee -&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt; The trivia will work like this... I will paste a question in the channel. If you know the answer please send me a PM by typing /msg Brekkee your answer here &lt;BR&gt;&lt;FONT color=#800000&gt;&lt;B&gt;Brekkee -&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt; The first five correct responses will get a cd key for the upcoming expansion &lt;BR&gt;&lt;FONT color=#800000&gt;&lt;B&gt;Brekkee -&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt; If I say your name as one of the five correct responses please stick around until I message you for information &lt;BR&gt;&lt;FONT color=#800000&gt;&lt;B&gt;Brekkee -&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt; Here we go! &lt;BR&gt;&lt;FONT color=#800000&gt;&lt;B&gt;Brekkee -&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt; Question: What is the name of the item that will allow you to shape-shift &lt;BR&gt;&lt;FONT color=#800000&gt;&lt;B&gt;Brekkee -&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt; into a creature in Depths of Darkhollow? &lt;BR&gt;&lt;FONT color=#800000&gt;&lt;B&gt;Brekkee -&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt; and we have our five winners! &lt;BR&gt;&lt;FONT color=#800000&gt;&lt;B&gt;Brekkee -&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt; The correct answer of course was Spirit Shroud. &lt;BR&gt;&lt;FONT color=#800000&gt;&lt;B&gt;Brekkee -&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt; Redi, Leeroy, Noryn, Tettsuro, and Fanose I will be contacting you shortly. Don't go anywhere and congratulations! &lt;BR&gt;&lt;FONT color=#800000&gt;&lt;B&gt;Brekkee -&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt; Thank you everyone for joining us tonight! &lt;BR&gt;&lt;FONT color=#0000a0&gt;&lt;B&gt;Prathun -&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt; I'll be over in #EverQuest if anyone has any other questions. Thanks again for coming tonight! &lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;</description>
